decks.notes: This deck aims to apply early pressure while disrupting the opponent's game plan. It includes a combination of efficient creatures like Deathrite Shaman and Orcish Bowmasters, along with disruptive cards like Lavinia, Azorius Renegade and Force of Will to counter spells. The deck also utilizes card advantage through cantrips like Ponder and Preordain, as well as the powerful draw spells Ancestral Recall and Dig Through Time. With a mix of efficient removal in Swords to Plowshares and Prismatic Ending, and mana acceleration from Moxen and Lurrus of the Dream-Den, the deck aims to maintain control while applying pressure.
